My 12 yr old daughter and I stopped in to pick up some specific shorts that she has fallen in love with and we just “needed” another pair. The store had rearanged some of the summer clothing and we couldnt find them. No worries though, we found some other shorts that we thought would do the trick. 
We mention at checkout that we were hoping to find a certain pair and the cashier gave us the directions to where they had moved to. Unfortunately, they didnt have the size we needed so when we returned to checkout, the cashier took the time to look online and helped us order the exact color and size we were looking for!
The employees at the Merle Hay Mall location were so helpful, pleasant, and just good people. We will not only be back, but I will make a point to start our back to school shopping there next month!  Thank you!
